"{\"uid\": \"bleacherreport.com-articles-10131376-olympic-breakdancing-2024-results-womens-breaking-medal-winners-and-highlights\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Breakdancing made its debut at the 2024 Paris Olympics, with B-girl Ami of Japan winning the inaugural breaking gold medal on Friday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 133, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 75, \"end\": 80, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_baseball_team\", \"score\": 0.9459627457608741, \"rank\": 0.04450568437792648, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_baseball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_baseball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ami, whose legal name is Ami Yuasa, defeated Lithuania's B-girl Nicka (Dominika Banevi\\u010d) in the gold medal battle.\", \"from\": 135, \"to\": 249, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 180, \"end\": 189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999408828, \"rank\": 5.894624870486502e-11, \"text\": \"Lithuania\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, B-girl 671 of China (Liu Qingyi) took down B-girl India of the Netherlands in the bronze battle to earn a spot on the podium.\", \"from\": 250, \"to\": 386, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 275, \"end\": 280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999991969055869, \"rank\": 7.5235671010043e-07, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 286, \"end\": 292, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qingyi_River_(Sichuan)\", \"score\": 0.6010059089231704, \"rank\": 0.4444444444444482, \"text\": \"Qingyi\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qingyi_River_(Sichuan)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qingyi_River_(Sichuan)\"}, {\"begin\": 311, \"end\": 316, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.6205420961772213, \"rank\": 0.607904509138533, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\"}, {\"begin\": 324, \"end\": 335, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_baseball_team\", \"score\": 0.9231477633760442, \"rank\": 0.08041410419679001, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_baseball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_baseball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Medal Winners  Gold: Ami Yuasa, Japan  Silver: Dominika Banevi\\u010d, Lithuania  Bronze: Liu Qingyi, China  Yuasa finished the round-robin tournament to begin the competition without losing a single round.\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 588, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 420, \"end\": 425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_baseball_team\", \"score\": 0.9459627457608741, \"rank\": 0.04450568437792648, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_baseball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_baseball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 453, \"end\": 462, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999408828, \"rank\": 5.894624870486502e-11, \"text\": \"Lithuania\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 476, \"end\": 482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qingyi_River_(Sichuan)\", \"score\": 0.6010059089231704, \"rank\": 0.4444444444444482, \"text\": \"Qingyi\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qingyi_River_(Sichuan)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qingyi_River_(Sichuan)\"}, {\"begin\": 484, \"end\": 489, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999991969055869, \"rank\": 7.5235671010043e-07, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She advanced beyond the quarterfinals and semifinals before she faced Banevi\\u010d, winning all three rounds in the final battle.\", \"from\": 589, \"to\": 713, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite falling in the gold medal battle, Banevi\\u010d was excited to see the sport on the Olympic stage.\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 815, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Olympics needed breaking because it's like a breath of fresh air,\\\" she said, perNoreen Nasirof the Associated Press.\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 934, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 917, \"end\": 933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9990283764765541, \"rank\": 0.0009724492684606128, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Such a big amount of people saw breaking for the first time, like it's huge.\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 1012, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I am happy that I was able to represent at the highest level of the art form for breaking.\\\"\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1108, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The United States failed to exceed expectations in the competition, as B-girl Sunny and B-girl Logistx were both unable to advance beyond the round-robin stage.\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1270, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1114, \"end\": 1127, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.6943505491576458, \"rank\": 0.2896483313166541, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Logistx (Logan Edra) was still proud of her performance.\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1336, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel like I still shined and I feel like I still represented the dance and had some moments,\\\" she said, via Nasir.\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1455, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1449, \"end\": 1454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nasir\", \"score\": 0.6451136747594037, \"rank\": 0.33272970793526324, \"text\": \"Nasir\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nasir\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nasir\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was such a big opportunity, it's such a big platform, and I am really happy that we are here.\\\"\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1554, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Snoop Dogg also made an appearance on Friday, entering the Place de la Concorde before the battle started.\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1662, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1556, \"end\": 1566, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snoop Dogg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\"}, {\"begin\": 1615, \"end\": 1635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"score\": 0.9999051610814582, \"rank\": 9.484791370418877e-05, \"text\": \"Place de la Concorde\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The men's breaking competition is up next on Saturday, with the round-robin tournament beginning at 10 a.m.\", \"from\": 1664, \"to\": 1771, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ET.\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1775, \"entities\": []}]}"